d236b299-d040-4b53-9671-8ccc4124a6ed	384ae428-f077-418b-8f71-368cebe7df52	5957e16e-4fff-4fba-9813-e287310b2d2b	Support	client	Hello,r\nr\nI have already installed the SSL certificate on my website, but my domain is still not working. It seems that the DNS records are not properly added or configured, which is causing the issue.r\nr\nI also followed the steps in cPanel (SSL/TLS Status → Run AutoSSL), but the problem still persists.r\nr\nKindly check and properly configure the DNS settings for my domain so that the website can start working correctly with SSL.r\nr\nPlease resolve this issue as soon as possible.r\nr\nThank you.	{}	2026-03-17 08:45:14
37d5cdf5-bb64-4d22-a8f5-4486d1c01eaa	384ae428-f077-418b-8f71-368cebe7df52	5957e16e-4fff-4fba-9813-e287310b2d2b	Support	client	Hello,r\nr\nMy domain http://qureshitax.com/ is not opening at all. I have already installed SSL, but the website is still inaccessible.r\nr\nIt seems that the domain is not properly pointed to the hosting server (DNS issue). Kindly check and configure the correct DNS records or nameservers for my domain so that it can connect to the hosting and start working.r\nr\nPlease resolve this issue as soon as possible.r\nr\nThank you.	{}	2026-03-17 08:50:55
